OL,3,CUpgrading deadly road would breach
OL,4,Cgoal of cutting emissions court told
OL,6,FApproving part of the #1.2bn A5 road
OL,7,Fupgrade allegedly breaches a
OL,8,Flegislative goal for cutting
OL,9,Fgreenhouse gas emissions in Northern
OL,10,FIreland, the High Court heard today.
OL,12,FCounsel for a group of residents and
OL,13,Flandowners claimed it was irrational
OL,14,Fto give the go-ahead for the first
OL,15,Fphase of the dual carriageway scheme
OL,16,Fdue to the potential adverse impact on
OL,17,Fclimate change targets.
