OL,6,FThe 53-mile upgrade, which forms part
OL,7,Fof a proposed key cross-border
OL,8,Fbusiness route linking Dublin and the
OL,9,Fnorth west, has already been held up
OL,10,Fby previous legal actions.
OL,12,FAn umbrella body of landowners,
OL,13,Ffarmers and supporters known as the
OL,14,FAlternative A5 Alliance successfully
OL,15,Fchallenged earlier decisions to
OL,16,Fapprove the project in 2013 and again
OL,17,Fin 2018.
