OL,6,FFresh judicial review proceedings have
OL,7,Fbeen brought against the Department
OL,8,Ffor Infrastructure by nine individuals
OL,9,Fon behalf of the Alliance.
OL,11,FAs the hearing got underway, several
OL,12,Fhundred people took part in a rally
OL,13,Foutside the Royal Courts of Justice in
OL,14,Fsupport of the scheme.
OL,16,FThey included relatives of some of
OL,17,Fthose killed in crashes on the stretch
OL,18,Fof road.
