OL,3,CUpgrading deadly road would breach
OL,4,Cgoal of cutting emissions court told
OL,6,FThe barrister directed his initial
OL,7,Ffocus on the Climate Change (Northern
OL,8,FIreland) Act 2022, which contains a
OL,9,Fseries of interim targets moving
OL,10,Ftowards achieving net-zero emissions
OL,11,Fby 2050.
OL,13,FThe court heard how a Planning Appeals
OL,14,FCommission inquiry into the A5 upgrade
OL,15,Frecommended against proceeding with
OL,16,Fthe scheme unless the Department was
OL,17,Fsatisfied it would not undermine those
OL,18,Fgoals
