OL,3,CUpgrading deadly road would breach
OL,4,Cgoal of cutting emissions court told
OL,6,FCiting the already challenging climate
OL,7,Ftarget, he argued that construction
OL,8,Fwork and increased traffic on the new
OL,9,Froad could result in increased
OL,10,Fgreenhouse gas emissions.
OL,12,FThe net-zero objectives contained in
OL,13,Fthe Act are mandatory, he insisted.
OL,15,F"It is a legal imperative, unless (the
OL,16,FDepartment) can demonstrate with such
OL,17,Fprecision that it will not prevent or
OL,18,Fprejudice those statutory targets
OL,19,Fbeing met," Mr Willers added
