OL,4,Cgoal of cutting emissions court told
OL,6,FFurther grounds of challenge in the
OL,7,Fcase allege: a breach of planning
OL,8,Fregulations; a breach of habitats
OL,9,Fregulations by failing to take an
OL,10,Fappropriately precautionary approach
OL,11,Fto the impact on the Tully Bog
OL,12,Fconservation area; a failure to
OL,13,Ffurther consult the public; and a
OL,14,Fbreach of the group's Article 8 human
OL,15,Frights.
OL,17,FAs the hearing continued, a solicitor
OL,18,Ffor the Alliance also described the
OL,19,Fcase as an attempt to protect the
OL,20,Fenvironment and safeguard Special
OL,21,FConservation Areas.
