OL,3,CUpgrading deadly road would breach
OL,4,Cgoal of cutting emissions court told
OL,6,FSpeaking outside court, Ciaran O'Hare
OL,7,Fof McIvor Farrell said: "My clients
OL,8,Frespectfully submit that it would be
OL,9,Fmuch more pragmatic, less
OL,10,Fcontroversial and ecologically-sound
OL,11,Fto upgrade the existing A5 road.
OL,13,F"Northern Ireland is already one of
OL,14,Fthe most nature-depleted countries in
OL,15,Fthe world... to literally bulldoze
OL,16,Fnature and permanently scar the land
OL,17,Fwould be unethical and a cause for
OL,18,Fgreat regret."
